<span class="p">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="Trail"/><category term="Posting"/><category term="One"/><category term="Trail"/><category term="Posting"/><category term="One"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Basic GitHub blog positing structure with image, audio, video, and comments options]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Impacts of renewable energy on the upcoming power crisis in Bangladesh</title><link href="https://rayid-mojumder.github.io/blog/2019/impacts-of-renewable-energy-on-the-upcoming-power-crisis-in-bangladesh/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Impacts of renewable energy on the upcoming power crisis in Bangladesh"/><published>2019-09-08T16:30:41+00:00</published><updated>2019-09-08T16:30:41+00:00</updated><id>https://rayid-mojumder.github.io/blog/2019/impacts-of-renewable-energy-on-the-upcoming-power-crisis-in-bangladesh</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://rayid-mojumder.github.io/blog/2019/impacts-of-renewable-energy-on-the-upcoming-power-crisis-in-bangladesh/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author></entry></feed>